messages.content: We want you help in reaching out to more people, so more people can benefit. Both sellers and buyers.

We have setup a platform called 1acre.in to help people with buying and selling of lands in telanagna. We verify all the lands that are listed. Buyers can contact the sellers directly. We don't charge a commission.
